content: Great app I definitely recommend having it installed on your phone

The fastest customer service you'll ever see. I researched through out google play store and no other app out there matches the SMS from this designer . By for the most editable and complex app and the power for your own imagination . GET IT NOW, ps make sure you edit the SMS into the star strek launcher in edit mode . Every app in the suite is worth five stars. The ease of access and level of customization are the best. Also one the greatest customer service experiences. Fans should be pleased.
Yeah! Finally, after having a dedicated SMS app for the LCARS theme we have now one for New Trek! Gorgeous, fully functional 5 star app! Many thanks!
